Author Jeewantha

This is a collection of Scripts that can make the life of a linux user easy. 

Core- will have implimentations of the hacks
Variables- will have global variables used in the scripts and the environmental variables needed in software applications.
Repository- will have other files needed for hacks.
Utils- will have utility scripts.
